docs {
  # List reworks in localized format
  
  ## Endpoint
  
  ```http
  GET https://connect.homag.cloud/api/productionManager/orders/reworks
  ```
  
  ## Purpose
  
  List rework entries using localized serialization so property names and enum values are returned in the requested culture.
  
  ## Parameters
  
  | Name | In | Type | Required | Description |
  |------|----|------|----------|-------------|
  | `format` | query | string | yes | Set to `localized` (case-insensitive) to enable localized output. |
  | `culture` | query | string | no | Localization culture (for example `de`, `en`, `de-DE`). Falls back to current server culture if omitted. |
  
  ## Request example
  
  ```http
  GET https://connect.homag.cloud/api/productionManager/orders/reworks?format=localized&culture=de
  ```
  
  ## Success response example
  
  ```json
  [
    {
      "Kundenname": "Customer GmbH",
      "L�nge": 733.62,
      "Breite": 362.75,
      "Nachfertigungs-ID": "d26bbb17-28ec-4382-a800-5cab99dcadd0",
      "ID": "16481767",
      "Beschreibung": "Inset Door",
      "Auftragsname": "Multi Shelf",
      "Material": "P2_Olive_green_19.0",
      "Anzahl Nachfertigungen": 1,
      "Kategorie": "Kantenanleimen",
      "Grund": "Nachfertigung nicht OK",
      "Status": "Abgelehnt",
      "Erfasst am": "2026-02-27T09:33:58.7831281+00:00",
      "Erfassungsdetails": {
        "Notizen": "",
        "Erfasst von": null,
        "Letzter Arbeitsplatz": "Dividing",
        "Letzter Arbeitsplatz-ID": null,
        "Anh�nge": []
      },
      "Ablehnungsnotiz": {
        "Abgelehnt am": "2026-02-27T09:34:10.4207612+00:00",
        "Abgelehnt von": "Boris Wehrle",
        "Notizen": "still  usable",
        "Anh�nge": []
      }
    }
  ]
  ```
  
  ## Possible error codes
  
  - `400 Bad Request` - Invalid query parameter values (for example unsupported `format` or invalid `culture`).
  - `401 Unauthorized` - Missing or invalid credentials, or required productionManager license is missing.
  - `500 Internal Server Error` - Unexpected server-side error.
  
  ## C# sample
  
  ```csharp
  using HomagConnect.Base.Extensions;
  using HomagConnect.ProductionManager.Client;
  
  var subscriptionId = Guid.Parse("<your-subscription-id-guid>");
  var authorizationKey = "<your-authorization-key>";
  
  var client = new ProductionManagerClient(subscriptionId, authorizationKey);
  
  var reworks = await client.GetReworks(
      states: null,
      take: 1000,
      skip: 0);
  
  var localizedJson = reworks.SerializeLocalized(System.Globalization.CultureInfo.GetCultureInfo("de"));
  Console.WriteLine(localizedJson);
  ```
  
  ## PowerShell sample
  
  ```powershell
  $baseUrl = "https://connect.homag.cloud"
  $subscriptionId = "<your-subscription-id>"
  $authorizationKey = "<your-authorization-key>"
  
  $pair = "{0}:{1}" -f $subscriptionId, $authorizationKey
  $encoded = [Convert]::ToBase64String([Text.Encoding]::ASCII.GetBytes($pair))
  
  $headers = @{
    Authorization = "Basic $encoded"
  }
  
  $url = "$baseUrl/api/productionManager/orders/reworks?format=localized&culture=de"
  $response = Invoke-RestMethod -Method Get -Uri $url -Headers $headers
  
  $response | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 10
  ```
  
  ## Referenced types (GitHub)
  
  - [ProductionManagerClient](https://github.com/HomagGroup/HOMAG-Connect/blob/main/Applications/ProductionManager/Client/ProductionManagerClient.cs)
  - [Rework](https://github.com/HomagGroup/HOMAG-Connect/blob/main/Applications/ProductionManager/Contracts/Rework/Rework.cs)
}
